jlb6740 commented on issue #5427:

@abrown .. It looks like your performance attempt /bench_x64 didn't run properly because the patch was already merged by the time the runner was picked up (even though you initiated the test before the run). A step in this action is to fetch all of the pull requests and check that request out after matching with the request id in the GITHUB_CONTEXT. In this case it was looking for 5427 but the pull request for 5427 did not exist. Look at the time stamps .. it looks like your job was picked up at "2022-12-13T20:06:14Z" while the patch was merged at about that time. I don't see the exact timestamp but it looks like your request came in ~hour later the patch was merged. The action was picked up about ~1 after your requested.
